Optional Features
-----------------

|Product| offers the highest level of scalability in the entire products portfolio. It can be configured with any of the three CPUs offered. Furthermore, both resistive and 
capacitive touch screen options are available for this product. 

Feel free to contact Chipsee technical support at |email|_ for all your customization needs.

|product| does not include WiFi/BT and/or 3G/4G modules by default. These modules are optional and can be selected at the Chipsee store during 
the ordering process. 

.. warning::   

   | Installation, repair, and maintenance tasks should be performed by trained personnel only.
   | Chipsee does not bear any responsibility for damage caused by inadequate handling of the product.